main event: Sighting of a vertical solid black object observed at Thule AB, Greenland on 5 Sep 1960.
interesting points: The object was observed at an estimated elevation of 10-15 degrees and was less than 100 ft away,No sound was reported during the observation, The sighting lasted approximately 4 minutes, Investigation into the sighting was deemed inconclusive, This event was documented under the USAF's Project Blue Book.
